                        <h2>托管磁盘<span>Managed Disks</span></h2>
                        <h4>用于 Azure 虚拟机的永久且安全的磁盘存储</h4>
                        <em><a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="home_site_trial_storage-Managed-Disks">申请试用<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></em>
                        <a href="/pricing/pia/" id="home_site_pia_storage-blobs">立即购买<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
